INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (17, 'Página 17', 'para chegar a um ou outro lugar. O lado imaterial da questão, por sua vez, dispensa qualificações ou aptidões especiais, que poderiam até mesmo prejudicar se acompanhadas de atrofia dos demais campos do conhecimento. O caráter de universalidade de que se reveste a cibernética é condicionado pela integração de todos os campos do saber, o que implica, para seus aficionados de qualquer nível, a posse de uma razoável dose de cultura geral e pressupõe o emprego de mentes abertas para o diálogo e livres de condicionamentos ou rótulos ideológicos.

A segunda particularidade que me animou a escrever este livro diz respeito à inexistência de obra de autor brasileiro, por tal motivo atento à nossa realidade econômica e cultural, que trate da cibernética em seu conteúdo global, sem dissociá-la do contexto no qual a "Ciência da comunicação, e do controle no animal e na máquina" se insere, que é o contexto dos sistemas. Talvez seja esta a causa de não se contar, no Brasil, até hoje, com uma cadeira de "Cibernética e Sistemas" em nossas universidades. E esta é a minha modesta contribuição, na certeza de que se trata de assunto básico', '[0.019518062,0.057226717,-0.060083598,-0.057909213,-0.067486614,-0.05118874,0.040510606,0.033592116,0.05771082,0.036382794,0.11330516,-0.03725365,-0.018902903,-0.019046843,-0.0039696977,-0.010111586,0.0016733394,0.044494003,-0.07504793,0.04711945,0.085184105,-0.055560526,-0.07711084,0.084224686,-0.11768794,0.0035094365,-0.020307701,-0.04582042,-0.05985931,-0.027222833,0.002434689,0.042135894,0.10238298,-0.013692465,0.010210873,0.025830857,0.031754524,-0.040172756,-0.009849682,0.07872701,-0.05193857,-0.022019316,-0.02952831,-0.04009302,-0.052180506,-0.025860231,0.07097203,0.06890729,-0.013723857,-0.005149534,-0.03365665,0.030147178,-0.050069124,0.020618387,0.012787865,-0.04546302,0.01808802,-0.0042011687,0.04240197,0.013133991,0.03014621,-0.009273689,5.415937e-05,0.029031912,0.034566987,-0.0051458124,-0.007043162,0.0036993315,-0.013668157,-0.015862077,0.07657143,-0.08594079,0.06224866,0.018750226,-0.043423876,0.10116596,-0.019291261,0.0032348784,-0.07874275,-0.11456495,0.061178345,0.040092114,-0.020498192,-0.06788619,0.016311191,-0.018186277,0.0066446303,0.033827268,0.033957448,0.0107111875,-0.009370021,0.049132094,-0.07469731,-0.070825584,-0.007405906,0.009383456,-0.009771197,-0.11041116,0.03158835,-0.016114376,0.09663248,-0.011293301,0.01897879,-0.03126367,-0.04567211,0.010078674,-0.046496294,-0.025174623,0.035555907,0.14452587,-0.13258506,-0.027932277,-0.0916868,-0.013499664,0.00666