INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (14, 'PREFÁCIO DO AUTOR', '# PREFÁCIO DO AUTOR

A idéia de escrever este livro nasceu no final da década de sessenta, embora de forma ainda vaga e imprecisa, ao ler "Admirável Mundo Novo", de Aldous Leonard Huxley. Qual a implicação dessa obra — um romance satírico com a cibernética, de que eu possuía então informações apenas superficiais, somente mais tarde emergiria em meu pensamento; o que foi fruto da intuição, entretanto, passou desde logo a motivar-me para a pesquisa em torno desse assunto.

A antevisão de uma sociedade ultra-estável apesar de constituída de seres humanos — imprevisíveis em seus desígnios e a partir de certo ponto ingovernáveis como entidades dotadas de discernimento e livre-arbítrio — somente seria possível sob um novo conceito de organização. O admirável mundo novo, realização da utopia pela Ciência, consiste de um mecanismo preciso e ajustado, como o de relojoaria — atente-se para o fato de que Huxley era filosoficamente mecanicista — cujos componentes, imitan', '[-0.06024993,0.051411077,-0.03573379,0.0029306102,-0.052764338,-0.016569369,0.039492626,0.04174517,0.038598284,0.07397083,0.011960496,-0.027735075,-0.025932793,-0.019208305,-0.035578553,0.0061147385,-0.026342407,-0.006641153,9.315878e-05,0.104954086,0.15198578,-0.04978861,-0.083225444,0.09011575,-0.050268482,0.032753613,-0.020362914,-0.012881535,-0.0349298,-0.00594045,0.013648107,0.017000778,0.13645016,-0.07946185,-0.023248227,0.07097469,0.045545377,-0.022724388,0.0421913,-0.019202143,-0.074791886,-0.038896002,-0.06491878,-0.012235143,-0.009062333,-0.010014293,0.0077351737,0.028425552,-0.034447208,-0.08499191,-0.14012852,-0.031463895,-0.045999218,-0.08091354,-0.018620186,-0.038912438,-0.013570255,0.011420653,0.04725294,-0.02389402,0.02088609,0.013067654,0.002317464,0.07358031,0.050326344,0.04133694,0.025542522,-0.004484674,-0.011368515,0.033484902,0.1264649,-0.06120067,0.034932412,-0.032517437,0.0059499335,0.060603708,-0.068565406,-0.011375584,-0.03149735,-0.099365875,0.026480893,0.01575264,-0.06131619,-0.007452682,0.0027689212,0.026280062,-0.022103982,-0.022037134,0.030455621,-0.0017065349,-0.061559755,-0.034956478,-0.12765495,0.013412973,0.047989443,-0.019533277,-0.029872812,-0.016541127,0.027604617,-0.013109504,0.070395924,0.07303885,0.012684478,0.0316951,0.03163972,-0.04986932,-0.020452144,-0.05149305,0.03206705,0.15191884,-0.09714544,-0.049523555,-0.052396286,0.0010171025,0.012925691,-0.010069844,-0.009016519,-0.051204085,0.05182462,-0.017497104,0.037180144,-0.08595711,