INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (42, 'Página 42', 'entre si. Interação é, por via de consequência, outra condição.

Coisas que se inter-relacionam e interagem, ou estão integradas, ou acabarão por integrar-se. Integração é, obviamente, a terceira condição. Fácil torna-se inferir que se trata de "conditio sine qua non", isto é, deixando de se verificar uma ou duas das condições, o conjunto não constituirá um sistema.

Estruturalmente os sistemas podem ser físicos (SF) ou de gestão (SG).

Sistema Físico é um conjunto coerente de coisas capaz de, em função de sua estrutura, ser orientado para propósitos.

Sistema de Gestão é um conjunto coerente de coisas adrede estruturado para operar um sistema físico orientando-o para os propósitos que o condicionam.

---

*(continuação) Parece-nos, ainda, que o conceito de teleonomia tornará mais completa a definição de sistema: "um conjunto coerente de coisas, dotado da propriedade teleonômica (Ver nota 4, Cap. I).*', '[0.014529692,0.042593498,-0.10451138,-0.048633263,-0.058197338,-0.033467557,0.0007153147,0.06245689,-0.00062021374,0.02988477,0.077261925,-0.038738858,0.007845592,0.013651068,0.035083383,-0.018522773,0.028032586,0.0027531271,-0.040423144,0.054137386,0.12923653,-0.051593076,-0.07866439,0.029266039,-0.10188611,0.05901076,0.013648,0.00796822,-0.025272744,-0.07752037,-0.051863737,-0.010206897,0.053439043,-0.0022337502,-0.0046231314,-0.030807583,0.08005347,-0.08959325,-0.00040291887,0.09021961,-0.12033309,0.03335715,-0.055029858,-0.056026444,-0.0048004426,-0.04512996,0.02451806,-0.0036657955,-0.036869656,-0.07599875,-0.0924991,0.004365168,-0.09871755,0.039921187,-0.016153334,0.029907307,-0.008834582,0.014263845,-0.004239157,0.00076794234,0.03684622,-0.0284442,0.021783948,0.071713835,-0.0082167005,0.016655538,0.045301042,0.024192898,-0.00855434,0.009489844,0.007205373,-0.03189176,-0.009456915,0.0487914,-0.018908473,0.092518814,0.030232707,0.049985163,0.011071846,-0.07634508,-0.018553868,0.033059277,-0.0670518,-0.041715764,0.083159834,-0.008498969,-0.0663417,0.039255016,6.290558e-05,0.032453045,0.024429081,0.055824008,-0.05588026,-0.13566007,0.115320414,0.033762213,0.028746815,-0.03191627,0.048464987,-0.038198654,0.06267224,0.016772212,-0.033651683,-0.00046509225,-0.027891155,0.029765848,0.040680043,0.0014256373,0.020904308,0.095566094,-0.07556748,-0.042333256,-0.053221453,-0.08941622,-0.061048314,0.019421775,0.09026178,0.0132652195,0.09267246,-0.017887473,0.012559686,-0.07952115,0.023596969,-0.012404891,0.077869885,-0.006544842,0.010254738,8.483337e-33,-0.06160622,-0.037505195,-0.041217726,-0.06638442,-0.07920538,0.03978107,-0.037100494,-0.0015883915,-0.020848123,0.06465815,-0.0788646,0.08180143,-0.022974284,-0.029488016,0.10794683,0.021591835,0.018893132,0.002973409,-0.048