INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (26, 'CAPÍTULO I', '# CAPÍTULO I

## BIOGRAFIA DO CONTROLE

### INTRODUÇÃO

Os biólogos sempre se preocuparam com o controle, considerado como uma função básica do organismo animal. Esta questão continua sendo objeto de estudos, cada vez mais profundos, em busca do completo conhecimento do "modus operandi" de tal mecanismo e de suas reais implicações na dinâmica da vida. Seja por auto-regulação fisiológica, seja através de respostas conscientes, volitivas, aos estímulos aferidos pelo mecanismo sensório, o controle, operando em tempo real, corrige, quando necessário, o ritmo metabólico, modifica hábitos e costumes, enfim, busca sempre a máxima adaptação do indivíduo ao habitáculo físico e ao meio social da espécie, melhor garantia de sua permanência no contexto biológico.', '[-0.011870625,0.020457566,-0.026659189,0.002510976,-0.008417886,-0.020280875,0.048654135,0.08474402,-0.022482451,0.07037314,0.064673945,-0.058459748,0.0024165518,0.043069515,-0.049172483,0.014942275,0.061451163,0.064960256,-0.020728996,0.08878166,0.18484384,-0.02616682,0.0014552089,0.056175612,-0.14986137,0.006725233,-0.055484813,-0.03199682,-0.04061959,-0.048450805,-0.04474738,0.087670416,0.118991695,-0.07946011,-0.011838167,0.024943545,0.03494003,-0.10042956,0.016064458,0.07425302,-0.088078156,-0.056566343,-0.06209404,-0.06908999,-0.055276763,-0.011791703,0.01159784,0.007230991,0.015745178,-0.07694881,-0.09345975,-0.009788718,-0.048673745,-0.019002605,0.050374422,-0.021249866,-0.007936125,-0.005587685,0.035887007,-0.046411734,0.006826647,0.03196977,-0.0027393308,0.049046088,0.009470281,0.03712028,-0.044980943,0.00824302,-0.012924701,-0.019481532,0.07234791,-0.097411744,0.030152319,0.019670766,-0.0128549095,0.0701758,-0.02836706,0.038350817,0.003239172,-0.1078851,0.041186538,-0.011247398,0.023249444,0.0010766354,0.032808963,-0.000402564,-0.031156296,0.001806568,-0.010684934,0.056252625,-0.028748529,0.029918091,-0.08113632,-0.087228335,0.02695878,-0.035612285,-0.022395222,-0.0645054,0.09193641,-0.04986775,0.025420403,0.0050068297,-0.05107139,0.053155515,-0.025241548,-0.0