INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (45, 'Página 45', 'imbuído dos mais nobres propósitos científicos, produziu o imprevisível Mr. HYDE...

Maisum aspecto merece ser ressaltado: a caracterização de um sistema, segundo a complexidade de sua estrutura, decorre de uma avaliação objetiva, de aspectos físicos, tangíveis, enquanto que a caracterização de seu grau de certeza (incerteza) implica alta dose de subjetivismo na avaliação do potencial sistêmico e na compreensão de seu "modus operandi".

Examinemos um exemplo de cada caso, como um exercício de Lógica Cibernética que nos propiciará penetração na intimidade dos sistemas.

Não resta dúvida de que o bilhar é, estruturalmente, um sistema simples: três bolas de marfim, uma mesa retangular revestida de feltro, laterais limitadas por tabelas elásticas, um ou mais jogadores, munidos do instrumento adequado para a execução das jogadas e conscientes das regras do jogo. O propósito do sistema, critério básico para o julgamento de seu grau de determinação, é fazer com que, em cada jogada, a bola branca choque-se contra as duas bolas vermelhas.', '[0.0280998,-0.0201629,-0.039625168,-0.046827447,-0.044824462,-0.070156395,-0.0028284802,0.10079059,0.027437728,0.06781358,0.061964884,0.016818963,0.020530118,0.00067944836,0.0127726775,-0.025310192,0.020121075,0.008446637,-0.06754106,0.06709245,0.13922614,-0.08463383,-0.0771433,0.054591767,-0.04677198,0.10369022,-0.0111999875,-0.010977766,0.009133102,-0.084863916,-0.00023416433,0.13250765,0.101764515,-0.06366484,-0.03669622,0.024178915,0.08346822,-0.08843563,0.0086739585,0.015872465,-0.123707116,-0.030328616,-0.07863688,-0.07801358,-0.015412543,-0.037917588,0.014819832,0.0119777955,-0.043314844,-0.071382105,-0.13427776,0.008905089,-0.06719551,0.037895024,0.054006513,-0.040990826,0.013312573,0.015801413,0.011339416,-0.054230522,-0.038268875,0.06593819,-0.011340597,0.04187849,-0.015772656,0.02544621,-0.021328552,0.004325114,-0.014563403,-0.03853064,0.0766117,-0.07891762,0.011056874,0.043469477,-0.047362037,0.036162127,0.010261877,0.0075040543,-0.004166861,-0.068008155,-0.008714922,0.04775955,-0.008092213,-0.006327064,-0.006943729,0.042626016,-0.026442977,-0.016973054,-0.041443568,-0.001477769,-0.025085146,0.0024353736,-0.02768464,-0.051386714,0.08619115,0.011143339,-0.0337655,-0.074061014,0.09999791,-0.037815947,0.068910606,0.066172734,-0.0033417551,-0.012789432,-0.04804113,-0.054468855,0.011457564,-0.034487706,0.041037187,0.050294384,-0.10653838,-0.02965248,-0.10936086,-0.124859326,-0.058982857,-0.082841106,0.04610005,0.0005127916,0.06676646,-0.066952035,-0.016451912,-0.053385146,0.03656547,-0.026341658