INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (75, 'Página 75', 'Consideremos o sistema fechado, cuja condição inicial pode ser representada pelo modelo isomórfico da figura 7, do qual se sabe ainda, que consome duas unidades de energia para realizar uma transição.

> **[Figura 7 — Modelo isomórfico do sistema fechado com condição inicial C₁: caixa retangular contendo as expressões "Eₙ = 8   C₁" e "Eₚ = 2".]**

modelo, e do que se sabe respeito do sistema, depreende-se que:

- o potencial máximo que o sistema pode abrigar representa-se pela inequação: Eₙ ≤ 10, sendo Eₙ a energia armazenável;

- partindo da condição inicial C₁, em que Eₚ = 2 (a entropia Eₚ já degradou duas unidades de energia), o sistema poderá operar quatro transições,¹⁴ realizando uma única transformação.

---

14. *A condição inicial, C₁, representada por Eₚ = 2, poderia significar, por exemplo, a energia consumida por uma máquina para atingir a sua temperatura ideal de funcionamento, ou o lastro de combustível em um tanque, para que a bomba possa funcionar.*', '[-0.004908713,0.043614846,-0.0015872098,-0.04724501,-0.115041785,0.020613553,-0.06368998,0.17178942,0.034192007,0.059379965,0.07739134,-0.053151604,0.044119053,-0.0033106986,-0.001290954,-0.06623635,0.018002426,0.044716198,-0.04331392,0.05871952,0.1552379,-0.12360527,-0.06528328,0.06969797,-0.06723718,-0.0059546866,-0.044628683,0.044411708,-0.049161904,-0.09311823,-0.06854089,0.0066558984,0.061893094,-0.014349944,-0.030986909,-0.0023185387,0.09333556,-0.088169366,-0.066773534,0.024871437,-0.092555426,0.003652556,-0.042581286,-0.067996465,0.06612418,-0.09009908,0.017022142,0.018610459,-0.015303654,-0.0523725,-0.038512465,-0.0035690332,-0.037612323,0.014738723,0.03326685,-0.045440134,-0.009020843,-0.02679306,0.02672371,0.0033245594,-0.009715304,0.016467456,0.015518109,0.09235081,-0.013208715,-0.008275786,-0.0430888,-0.058396567,-0.0753541,0.059580587,-0.013337183,-0.09306805,-0.02809104,-0.048859525,0.00582558,0.058947425,0.015165435,0.029035356,-0.0009382064,-0.08313335,0.019549986,0.025009843,-0.0165427,-0.09714766,0.050738763,-0.005517206,-0.0037329714,-0.010800062,0.069708586,0.010897772,0.05650374,0.040093113,-0.07537803,-0.020156562,0.0874367,-0.0056831725,0.020226223,-0.008777242,-0.016729865,-0.004732842,0.057191674,0.033514313,0.0006377967,-0.0025079797,-0.008377973,-0.042580355,0.090130545,0.022342786,-0.021381117,0.002215008,-0.047486644,-0.08963954,-0.10756534,-0.058491513,-0.034625236,-0.011185238,-0.020737886,-0.03768094,0.034327276,-0.005300751,-0.02143447,-0.04392242,0.0043210112,-0.00965284,0.016612256,-0.022796903,0.019611694,1.0108393e-32,-0.111851074,-0.017202655,0.029457308,-0.046247255,0.02484695,0.06019459,-0.06439021,0.069818325,0.07250912,-0.012579893,-0.09210326,0.041352794,-0.0055399654,0.