## 2.7. Lei da Variedade Requerida

A Teoria da Informação, ao quantificar a entropia, estabeleceu um importante liame entre os sistemas físicos e os sistemas de gestão. Recordemos que sistema de gestão é um conjunto coerente de coisas, a drede arquitetado para operar um sistema físico orientando-o para os propósitos que o condicionam

Analisemos, dentro dessa ordem de idéias, algumas situações cotidianas:

— o pastor, tangendo seu rebanho para o aprisco, sob a fiel vigilância dos cães de guarda;

— o zangão, cônscio de sua autoridade tribal, fiscalizando, atentamente, o labor', '[0.0055041,0.019759808,-0.095680565,-0.09310054,-0.07965339,-0.04152585,-0.0078751845,0.08327535,0.07421329,0.059675217,0.052786008,0.01077991,0.028041974,5.2214164e-05,-0.011971168,-0.027218396,0.019666947,0.052358914,-0.046278615,0.028541004,0.16035773,-0.029407866,-0.06743785,0.025154615,-0.12403619,0.044244092,-0.03450809,-0.03169461,-0.010299011,-0.048073765,-0.026634708,0.04510572,0.07075142,-0.03707327,-0.0019959558,0.05531401,0.09113641,-0.05249039,-0.010393861,0.09021542,-0.11569538,0.030016389,-0.042610094,-0.05086838,0.037130877,-0.05181744,0.012760676,0.01047911,-0.0634772,-0.062766805,-0.12197006,0.04213808,-0.048392974,-0.0024354237,-0.028400132,0.03214181,-0.06421633,-0.049242057,-0.0044358023,-0.0048386236,-0.055963147,-0.022917705,0.01198619,0.049790673,-0.0006072392,0.029897045,-0.0067958045,-0.027275909,-0.01015913,0.045702614,0.013533949,-0.061288454,0.00061327487,-0.039017614,-0.014473971,0.080964096,0.050869245,-0.009153238,0.0147267915,-0.17185946,-0.0060962113,0.04272381,-0.014425483,-0.0341861,0.022853673,0.021545501,-0.05530266,0.02710959,0.04989787,0.025287509,0.058186676,0.019162925,-0.10694529,-0.072674334,0.11351263,0.040806144,-0.017224144,-0.045077622,0.047236394,0.0021863792,0.053440344,-0.00060250994,0.009052242,-0.0068476573,-0.017009664,0.014784184,0.024920333,-0.0052746767,0.040209696,0.06240974,-0.07057875,-0.015844516,-0.061335213,-0.07535472,-0.05368306,-0.018740475,0.059990954,-0.014710761,0.021763615,-0.042509757,-0.023805544,-0.049627416,0.029263658,0.009893357,0.08643664,-0.028616719,0.028388184,1.0734492e-32,-0.08310067,-0.054095957,-0.033607837,-0.03807309,-0.010831513,0.06184751,-0.06578162,-0.023926996,0.023407958,0.103657074,-0.08710165,0.08198026,-0.093781166,0.0060867663,0.099347085,-0.004325653,0.033342935,-0.013648143,-0.08233583,-0.043191914,-0.010526337,0.026405105,0.0022856724,0.019974682,0.008100459,0.09578074,0.0077005625,-0.0