INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (200, '2.2. Aprestamento do Modelo', 'vel, situado em informática, ligado permanentemente ao eixo de comando central, que passa pelo vice-presidente executivo e através do qual transitam os interceptores.

No modelo neurofisiológico, diríamos que informática exerceria a função do diencéfalo, enquanto que controller atuaria como o centro de controle bulbar, inibindo e excitando o vago-simpático em busca de um permanente equilíbrio sinérgico. Em quaisquer dos dois casos, a ação motora se faz, repetimos, através do eixo de comando central — a medula — vice-presidente executivo.

### 2.2. Aprestamento do Modelo

O aprestamento do modelo de administração industrial implantado na ALPHA – Implementos Industriais-SA implica atividades de planejamento, programação e controle da produção.

O primeiro elemento da administração, segundo Fayol, é a previsão, do qual a pedra de toque é o programa de ação. Costuma-se antepor um elemento à programação — o planejamento da Produção — o que faz com que a previsão se desdobre em planeja', '[0.012311365,-0.04136137,-0.07235802,-0.075986944,-0.07391095,0.04197448,-0.0070170355,0.11429119,0.0060772942,0.11413428,0.06417781,0.032002777,0.05313489,-0.02368955,-0.04868058,-0.005361896,0.038646653,-0.044028,-0.019808622,0.042978246,0.1715751,-0.012877201,-0.03074844,0.038935646,-0.18541777,-0.008032013,-0.025434505,-0.022722004,-0.06427132,-0.08706214,-0.024410337,-0.019246077,0.047053277,-0.023198053,-0.029733587,-0.04138491,-0.046770714,-0.037491467,-0.007689018,0.0043658013,-0.042116724,-0.053276345,-0.045092236,-0.069782495,0.032064725,0.05941055,0.059247643,-0.0015663526,-0.026104782,-0.07900049,-0.02159718,-0.063244276,0.05710775,0.002966853,0.009089837,-0.048720855,-0.026368106,-0.012151223,-0.020575132,0.03727402,-0.019714233,0.044689734,-0.020838464,0.0010822876,0.009362456,-0.02257087,0.007549958,-0.04674222,-0.025339724,-0.0997116,0.008731374,-0.11179401,0.0019735764,-0.010927047,-0.016636545,0.032946818,0.0017180723,0.115140244,0.053768296,-0.14010455,0.08180513,0.03781977,-0.058124285,0.02426231,0.04257276,0.03159357,-0.031149812,-0.014834996,0.08089822,0.03157768,0.035653632,0.014029818,-0.029865272,-0.08508404,0.037117023,0.023667555,0.025818955,-0.036090177,0.0040551242,-0.013020062,0.03905577,0.0022936873,0.018301643,0.0003753692,-0.058813065,0.028748006,0.039974097,-0.044913515,0.039703924,0.040577676,-0.0678137,-0.00091611163,-0.1137464,-0.057324924,-0.010320689,-0.006633366,-0.03366633,-0.046298362,0.02633553,-0.047357745,0.00022743361,-0.12834002,0.032157928,-0.047277357,0.062054146,0.024715073,0.0133386385,8.873213e-33,-0.09007586,-0.04880954,-0.052807044,-0.019385366,-0.033488646,0.013974576,-0.028530551,0.034520593,0.11292613,-0.002114833,-0.12155121,0.043435153,0.026627524,0.05538923,0.1014498