INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (207, '2º Passo – Isolamento dos Centros de Custos', 'Os níveis de agregação do produto recebem referências numéricas que permitem particularizar os centros de custos pelos quais transitam os itens de materiais e as TE, tornando possível a futura integração da EDT ao plano de contas.

#### 2º Passo – Isolamento dos Centros de Custos

A dinâmica da contabilidade gerencial baseia-se nos centros de custos, unidades funcionais elementares da administração industrial. Por eles transitam todos os itens e TE que se agregam para formar o produto acabado.

Os centros de custos qualificam-se em auxiliares —CCA— e de produção (CCP).

Os centros de custos da produção, constituem microssistemas produtivos no interior dos quais conjuntos coerentes de itens de materiais e tarefas elementares integram-se, inter-relacionam-se e interagem com o propósito de atingir determinado nível de agregação do produto, fixado na definição do trabalho (mais especificamente, na EDT). Pelos CCP transitam somente', '[-0.02354797,-0.042713135,-0.04282174,-0.04290208,0.0016481068,0.017031768,-0.009047962,0.08354859,-0.0043402715,0.011210827,0.046859417,-0.11024781,-0.02081197,-0.024878226,-0.029643184,-0.0649529,0.032334156,0.023782484,-0.020130128,0.03813733,0.11094347,-0.054602847,-0.07084128,0.028997846,-0.07391566,0.026085073,-0.061886124,0.015718404,-0.031216357,-0.086625814,-0.07088733,0.050089743,0.11195773,0.0055840802,0.066539146,0.011551215,0.012563108,-0.036780898,-0.024757002,0.014613255,0.01486336,0.0022398108,0.020905366,-0.058677416,0.010952163,0.017593993,0.114723116,-0.0014156732,-0.029097132,-0.06809434,0.011138309,-0.0011648011,-0.067363694,0.08331486,-0.0030155987,0.0031437671,0.03858728,-0.028577834,0.022144182,0.0173005,0.042760514,-0.042645387,-0.013852183,-0.011225848,0.017564524,-0.03156936,-0.03816103,0.051280633,-0.109191865,0.019040842,0.058429975,-0.037965275,-0.052532766,0.08155352,0.0030772842,0.1405766,0.042778,0.009926411,-0.0004229747,-0.086514294,-0.024391353,0.10201756,-0.045109287,-0.062195513,0.0092893,0.03132092,0.009399285,0.016521899,0.047674194,-0.02614667,-0.0038340208,0.07144702,-0.11307228,-0.050536424,0.01794081,-0.0047123125,-0.015505078,-0.086779706,0.0654397,-0.07024429,0.08807486,0.056106895,0.03867378,-0.046918333,-0.08488875,0.025581094,-0.064720795,0.008257179,0.07035618,0.1382401,-0.07413239,-0.018716201,-0.09519034,-0.032965854,-0.08880442,-0.00927006,-0.0029695684,-0.07473957,0.061028045,-0.074225694,-0.008953289,-0.091196805,-0.00015830029,-0.009149073,0.014076852,0.025012756,0.071666054,8.813393e-33,-0.13013327,-0.09807191,0.012734054,-0.0070019374,0.018639283,-0