INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (159, 'Página 159', 'linhas pontilhadas.

O eixo de comando central trabalha com informação volitiva, de comando; o eixo de comando leteral, informação servomotora autônoma.

No primeiro nível, operação, preponderaram as ações do vago-simpático, excitando e inibindo a dinâmica das partes componente do sistema físico em busca do equilíbrio homeostático. Mas Op tem, à sua disposição, no eixo de comando central, canais para o trânsito de informações ascendentes/descendentes, podendo deflagrar ações motoras, volitivas, em decorrência de estímulos nociceptivos aferidos através dos interoceptadores. Qualquer estímulo nociceptivo, aferido em Op, passará pelo seguinte processamento²³.

— em primeiro lugar, será objeto de filtragem, nos sensores, a fim de ser enquadrado no respectivo conjunto afim de variáveis; dessa filtragem resultará substancial redução de variedade;

---

²³. *As três ações são, praticamente, simultâneas, mesmo porque o sistema precisa operar em tempo real.*', '[0.028226549,-0.020800354,-0.046314128,-0.012939413,-0.047490582,-0.030413987,0.07761185,0.13512604,0.06081844,0.054392632,0.07853291,-0.01959799,0.043786183,0.003030762,-0.015052606,-0.013596522,0.07553315,0.012987764,-0.015594906,0.07068621,0.13336952,-0.038467683,-0.0459885,0.05117022,-0.15349591,0.035398096,-0.046782248,0.007014215,-0.094997786,-0.052476574,-0.03645763,0.008260388,0.059156768,-0.011855804,0.039873175,-0.040579747,-0.008388659,-0.0131153865,0.018478503,0.008763728,-0.05176748,-0.044261,-0.073557876,-0.039589103,0.023592426,0.018654943,0.043727048,0.023033146,-0.036580004,-0.0056827716,-0.045788717,-0.018157996,-0.019150808,0.064722136,-0.0439468,-0.09287738,-0.054758552,-0.04931316,-0.06223023,0.022328964,-0.04749252,0.042061593,0.0035378234,0.021769507,0.04479098,0.020913677,0.042176127,-0.06553163,-0.02707616,-0.02651482,0.03524037,-0.07647987,0.025692653,-0.024596171,-0.03077177,0.0044913106,-0.027520128,0.013876339,0.007017859,-0.09265383,0.06515833,0.016736005,-0.0042663803,-0.010394053,0.041789696,-0.010894217,-0.0007602636,0.019087551,0.023579367,0.006725845,0.009815808,-0.010766511,-0.14271282,0.001071103,0.082552984,0.01292633,-0.007946371,-0.026448442,0.02432492,-0.037336834,0.05018266,-0.026314681,0.0039464785,0.026299447,-0.03239358,0.048809785,0.051812775,-0.068471566,-0.0030336285,0.07659533,-0.11148016,-0.06096925,-0.058650445,-0.0235506,-0.05176354,0.0084643075,-0.04444232,0.0018283767,0.02332734,0.0015539477,-0.011045126,-0.083550826,-0.0033990734,-0.036108784,0.08090852,0.0011801241,0.06979686,1.2457194e-32,-0.04818056,-0.06460291,-0.003003942,-0.0071274573,-0.003449025,0.03422281,-0.030998133,0.042290434,0.0731271,-0.006084015,-0.09526851,0.07359284,0.03916885,0.021269253,0.04272567,-0.02148996,0.06699455,-0.063632995,0.041702636,-0.045694534,0.0014742865,0.0040445696,-0.009213002,0.010104496,-0.032383565,0.101597354,-0.0