INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (196, 'CAPITULO II', '## CAPITULO II

## ESTRATÉGIA ANTICRISE – O MODELO EM AÇÃO

### INTRODUÇÃO

A estratégia anticrise formulada pelo Projeto Alpha prevê a adequação da estrutura organizacional da empresa às novas relações de produção e a implantação de um sistema integrado de programação e controle da produção — SIPCP — calcado numa avaliação precisa do potencial produtivo.

A implementação da estratégia anticrise constitui objeto deste capítulo, e implica a adoção de um modelo cibernético de administração industrial, que será exposto em suas linhas gerais, uma vez que já é velho conhecido nosso, desde a primeira parte desta obra. A instituição de uma contabilidade gerencial — de que demos rápida notícia, ao final da primeira fase — será esmiuçada em seus detalhes, pois constitui a base teórica e prática sobre a', '[-0.0005724288,0.02826974,-0.034867853,-0.07575029,0.012613564,0.01844634,0.033545874,0.09020944,-0.016887624,0.086687215,0.06462514,-0.04583732,-0.017363278,-0.0055365325,-0.04076779,-0.046469484,0.04121111,-0.015536741,0.011084332,0.05404521,0.18513937,-0.06869294,-0.025328409,0.06414602,-0.08978824,0.03246862,-0.05147276,-0.009532166,-0.023049377,-0.052147828,-0.024946721,-0.009399019,0.17400919,-0.04249793,0.004160837,-0.013480816,0.020725388,-0.0068499744,0.029661939,0.07835212,-0.078802526,-0.07058344,-0.121180035,-0.10411957,0.0391213,-0.022854704,0.04297718,-0.00054680323,-0.033846367,-0.040474482,-0.027024508,-0.001990049,-0.02261678,-0.061756592,0.017000465,-0.071049124,0.0028234846,-0.039370157,-0.003571756,0.036514457,-0.048504166,0.050801337,-0.0304119,0.01530741,0.08528813,0.013584051,-0.055541564,0.042849403,-0.016568236,-0.0006719395,0.03452024,-0.035464674,0.018656394,-0.041259024,-0.011780809,0.07142298,-0.02253703,0.07697167,0.030991303,-0.09596058,0.045272537,-0.006727499,-0.03743914,-0.0132036265,-0.01657319,0.016219098,-0.034380168,0.0063700364,0.050817277,-0.020392723,-0.050832227,0.056076005,-0.04253214,-0.0009820615,0.07061401,0.018588662,0.00030746835,-0.04642454,0.014016469,-0.031978995,0.0063449335,0.002680547,-0.008756422,-0.074797586,0.006438244,-0.09330805,-0.024297128,-0.035728857,0.024368735,0.09308383,-0.013237229,-0.060348224,-0.12411453,-0.028624322,-0.02611519,-0.008901119,0.0013682741,-0.04914639,0.04626986,-0.0745494,0.037202302,-0.0900069,0.055929366,-0.029036243,0.03552902,0.030226754,