INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (249, 'Página 249', 'sideravelmente. Outro exemplo, talvez mais sugestivo, seria de um equipamento para ampliar fotografias (rede principal) acoplado a um dispositivo regulador de cores e tonalidades (rede de feedback) cuja sensibilidade de foto-elétrica excluísse as manchas (cores e tonalidades cuja intensidade estivesse fora dos padrões). Quanto maior a ampliação, mais perfeitas as fotografias.

A terceira e última inferência (fiquemos apenas com as principais) decorre, ainda, de um aspecto puramente matemático da g (t): o seu valor poderá ser positivo ou negativo, dependendo do resultado da relação 1 – f (t). f (T). Voltemos à segunda inferência: vimos que quando a função de transferência da rede principal f(t) cresce, tornando-se muito maior do que 1, o valor de g (t) tende a tornar-se independente de f (t) e negativo, ficando condicionado quase somente pela função de transferência da rede de feedback f(T). Vimos, ainda, que, em tais condições, o sinal de entrada poderá ser ampliado sem que qualquer ruído ou falsa informação se amplifique, o que torna a saída da maior pureza. Pois aí está a razão pela', '[-0.016498804,0.031173583,-0.025454227,-0.0493883,-0.014239031,0.0067997472,0.020282732,0.06947112,0.0073576733,0.07613089,0.1322088,-0.06343168,0.03005057,0.008460749,-0.0080469595,-0.032948986,0.061111003,0.05176614,-0.09011086,0.07832895,0.10915843,-0.11448557,-0.029885033,-0.007765012,-0.07248118,-0.03627288,-0.057479586,0.010754148,-0.034916602,-0.14809108,-0.04638112,0.032832976,0.10678448,-0.041312225,-0.02161905,0.07934959,0.007258707,-0.052042842,-0.0122191785,0.051659204,-0.10562832,-0.028725646,-0.09411216,-0.060879335,0.03414105,-0.01261946,0.1137118,0.072737,-0.026582666,-0.0073406394,-0.0030975146,0.044693757,-0.08632731,0.06681895,-0.018038552,-0.03256363,0.03177516,-0.032229252,0.024319919,0.0026246915,-0.003360518,0.021164667,-0.07235238,0.0075144786,0.088017225,-0.008796764,0.022447014,-0.08273594,-0.042484637,0.018653078,0.092200756,-0.058179572,0.016013144,0.007205765,-0.021300513,0.06450618,0.009326877,0.01922227,-0.041326057,-0.094851114,0.08339598,-0.008435604,0.0055363304,-0.029354367,0.032098733,-0.039390482,-0.044400763,0.019117264,-0.051766336,0.017190702,-0.029895151,0.060878247,-0.11250184,-0.08572822,0.0035946388,-0.033834133,-0.10009479,-0.055000402,0.12595978,-0.0074871494,0.07782921,0.0013046406,0.007884218,-0.019251766,0.