INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (201, 'Planejamento da Produção', 'mento e programação, ficando o ciclo da administração constituído de PLANEJAR, PROGRAMAR, COMANDAR, COORDENAR e CONTROLAR. Planejar e programar são duas atividades intimamente ligadas, pois a segunda é condicionada pela primeira. A programação se assenta sobre o planejamento, e constitui um método que, subordinado a parâmetros fixados sob a forma de variáveis essenciais e variáveis de ação, tem a finalidade de operacionalizá-lo.

Como o sistema integrado de programação e controle da produção está em seu estágio inicial, informática não dispõe, ainda, em seu banco de dados, dos subsídios necessários à programação da produção. Tais subsídios serão obtidos através do planejamento, primeira fase de aprestamento do modelo.

#### Planejamento da Produção

Na figura 26 — Grafo das Atividades de Planejamento da Produção, distingue-se cinco passos:

- 1º – Definição do Trabalho
- 2º – Isolamento dos Centros de Custos
- 3º – Integração de um Plano de Con', '[0.013520851,-0.020743998,-0.09365334,-0.082429364,-0.0667758,0.021550797,-0.016735243,0.11027154,-0.015302336,0.08857202,0.028111365,0.0023668956,-0.015755223,-0.016437618,-0.015378467,0.02349983,0.021007342,-0.045226462,-0.034889497,-0.0225824,0.16225475,0.023011236,-0.044331055,0.03946625,-0.08579468,0.0244485,0.008649453,0.0039801258,-0.048306815,-0.032817125,-0.008726062,0.028030178,0.15157406,0.009829709,0.010732298,-0.028351137,0.021649443,-0.060261346,-0.0087152375,0.03611811,-0.08528572,-0.0029070743,-0.04627429,-0.056738954,0.012259892,-0.021874443,0.0069618835,0.009991438,-0.032075025,-0.028458185,-0.064830676,-0.020312088,-0.009527946,-0.025047772,0.009643191,-0.056399778,0.036103703,0.02389785,-0.020810885,0.013799235,-0.05572921,0.068331756,-0.042909887,0.0056118565,0.0069630677,0.02092525,0.014231078,-0.022075113,-0.043029886,-0.083828926,-0.04574657,-0.043282676,0.012921264,0.026551459,-0.054059356,0.053436957,0.025013931,0.029092526,0.012192958,-0.1775876,0.021960387,0.051270448,-0.055763204,-0.00029515687,0.035758592,-0.026881095,-0.008616968,0.0049694823,0.031045664,0.052760713,0.024496432,0.017282307,-0.0035357513,-0.06888944,0.008624313,-0.0038069854,0.040466845,-0.114443146,0.04347659,-0.02545859,0.04217144,-0.033499308,0.030751472,0.00444356,-0.04618504,-0.02794016,0.08792057,-0.039337017,0.039769962,0.09874153,-0.12074772,0.0012111695,-0.113898456,-0.07672409,-0.05575249,-0.050190143,-0.046622377,0.013003899,0.00722514,-0.06153913,-0.047152188,-0.08847134,0.10379239,-0.026464174,0.023606783,-0.024471423,0.022267163,6.348182e-33,-0.07477783,-0.023705373,-0.053457882,-0.003799121,-0.0039741662,0.0325007,-0.01979975,0.0337399,0.049976755,0.021159476,-0.1149376,0.05249678,-0.037892163,0.037298184,0.18634197,-0.033204775,0.04828072,0.0034549234,-0.028733747,0.00752162,-0.007252419,-0.0052394946,0.05043658,-0.028633932,0.13569538,0.04565655,-0.03654986,-0.005263602,-0.09550358,0.039069816,0.07134995,0.0259515