INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (221, 'Página 221', 'da linha de oscilação, enquanto que a preocupação dos sistemas de gestão departamentais concentra-se nos respectivos pontos de ruptura da linha de sinergia. Este o motivo pelo qual frisamos, no capítulo terceiro da primeira parte, que controller é um generalista que atua "externa corporis".

Para encerrar, façamos uma rápida conjectura em torno do desvio observado em CCAO₈, cujas despesas com relações públicas e publicidade correspondem a um nível de desempenho da ordem de 160% (o que somente seria compatível, sinergicamente, com uma capacidade produtiva de 160% por parte de todos os departamentos da empresa!).

Os recursos alocados a CCAO, embora virtualmente escassos, eram satisfatórios, considerando-se o fato de que o mercado é comprador e ainda que a ALPHA detém o monopólio do produto. Assim, o papel de CCAO₈ seria, simplesmente, manter contato periódico com os clientes, sem necessidade de por em prática uma dispendiosa e agressiva política de marketing. A disfunção de', '[0.053901117,0.024760714,-0.12259621,-0.06652187,-0.031005232,0.0005556022,0.005644349,0.0566167,0.017221114,0.051101975,0.10880601,-0.055526305,-0.03965145,0.025542315,0.07208675,-0.03895321,0.013292218,0.02498644,-0.02041163,0.11295975,0.14973433,-0.03488277,-0.02797183,0.05650989,-0.11296004,0.002814513,0.015135439,-0.039462496,-0.056825224,-0.08229644,-0.006935474,-0.006078535,0.10719217,-0.027219417,0.010529585,0.00989157,0.06773398,-0.077428214,-0.050428823,0.07719386,-0.057732973,0.019187944,-0.08069939,-0.0639375,-0.024170883,-0.074528836,0.08322912,0.08032941,-0.014790546,-0.04852406,0.050529122,-0.012428459,-0.05459375,-0.008533445,0.0012402487,-0.062496174,-0.048371032,-0.02569457,-0.011400151,-0.014552046,0.02839108,0.028027065,0.0080133695,0.037107278,0.008862006,-0.04454613,0.038069066,-0.014939738,-0.07394156,-0.032549795,0.020276308,-0.07918359,-0.020953074,0.04310677,-0.038181897,0.07669939,0.019097997,0.07582543,0.034432158,-0.108622074,0.05247482,0.07258447,-0.016176943,0.025603697,0.010300207,0.015008129,-0.0060655097,0.026772367,0.041963622,-0.016691929,0.011025321,0.05218437,-0.09565845,-0.04805552,-0.0053286017,-0.03679021,0.047070295,-0.003749952,0.03876402,0.003683118,0.030951776,0.011418675,0.024843084,-0.084268086,-0.031896103,0.042121317,-0.0093718385,0.01337079,0.038112793,0.11166118,-0.13288182,-0.06801056,-0.13581131,-0.04451507,-0.014522848,-0.00047261664,-0.0466658,-0.053544912,0.03359322,-0.07121195,0.032234147,-0.07211041,0.049989223,-0.054473903,0.061077826,-0.05110758,0.024752125,8.885888e-33,-0.0892663,-0.071367994,-0.021739611,-0.011781368,0.040155265,0.010621163,