INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (228, 'Página 228', 'partida?

Já no século XVIII JOHN LOCKE reedita o pensamento de Platão, evidentemente que ajustado ao misticismo religioso da época: os empiristas reconhecem que "o simples testemunho da revelação constitui a mais alta certeza" ("revelação", para LOCKE, é o mesmo que intuição, e corresponde, de certa forma às idéias inatas, de Platão), e que "a revelação deve ser julgada pela razão". Cerca de um século mais tarde influenciado pelo pensamento de LOCKE, EMANUEL KANT escreve a "Crítica da Razão Pura", destinada a provar que, embora nada de nosso conhecimento possa transcender a experiência, é, não obstante, em parte, a priori, e, não, inferido indutivamente da experiência. O termo que emprega para exprimir esse conceito — "Anschauung" — traduz-se para o vernáculo como INTUIÇÃO.

Eis, aí, o traço de união entre o método racional — dedutivo e indutivo — e o que se pode, sem violar os princípios da lógica e do bom senso, chamar de método intuitivo.', '[-0.047723256,0.028625814,-0.039520435,0.03131292,-0.049248233,0.034985155,0.02743548,0.06153457,-0.020353839,0.099237025,0.04022336,0.008543644,-0.014673133,-0.028744083,-0.036703415,0.011897134,-0.019140994,0.08216685,-0.09116979,0.074098736,0.09920216,-0.012687824,-0.057547405,0.04277211,0.016833458,0.04322222,0.03293265,0.017547054,0.00780977,-0.018650413,-0.013258934,-0.014314966,0.090358295,-0.033626307,-0.012674695,0.07187981,0.06796159,-0.06611041,0.046882644,-0.00024990857,-0.07284984,0.05698424,-0.091808975,0.02062882,-0.013262214,-0.06250216,0.08093997,0.02664841,-0.057338122,-0.061771642,0.028863937,-0.027362598,-0.06371987,-0.029441927,-0.039539006,-0.041222643,-0.0071487515,-0.0063090795,0.005987071,0.0066995034,0.019406632,0.041722078,-0.024254296,0.026810043,-0.006132422,0.030455077,0.05987061,-0.048919853,-0.05219369,-0.028499195,0.068524405,-0.03134813,0.051993325,-0.017052427,-0.05192463,0.030952249,0.017583605,0.038422592,-0.071968816,-0.064871535,0.005770999,0.0021101737,-0.039600752,0.015396702,0.0036530357,-0.010295643,0.01878103,0.038097873,0.050859645,0.023024227,-0.015548845,0.010349931,-0.03321351,0.009495564,0.02107487,0.021184364,-0.008608436,-0.100360245,0.06804092,0.0018061725,0.02659492,0.11842515,0.02008103,-0.019230092,0.038262695,-0.09698851,-0.05680991,-0.05831111,-0.05748436,0.06549239,-0.044395316,-0.088154264,-0.051984083,-0.010523239,0.03154784,-0.035771895,0.037168913,0.0015306844,0.017832065,0.01855354,-0.0066340277,-0.053571012,0.009190642,0.03168882,0.049352333,-0.07554082,0.00721512,8.276835e-33,-0.03401987,-0.057282027,-0.07427537,0.039905366,-0.03419267,0.053128324,0.013681242,0.058708306,0.019002171,-0.009095297,-0.043419212,0.08337601,0.033009063,0.016260618,0.072723545,0.0330632,-0.04824438,-0.053235836,-0.0036668365,-0.05714519,-0.06961506,0.0291