INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (204, '1º Passo – Definição do Trabalho', 'tas à EDT
- 4º – Avaliação da Capacidade Produtiva
- 5º – Estimativa de Vendas

Examinemos cada um desses passos, de per si.

#### 1º Passo – Definição do Trabalho

O produto acabado, resultado do trabalho empreendido na empresa, consome dois insumos (input = entrada) básicos: a mão-de-obra e os materiais aplicados. Definir-se o trabalho, consequentemente, implica considerações em torno do processamento dos insumos.

Consideremos, inicialmente, a mão-de-obra aplicada ao produto. Ela é decomposta em unidades que demandam tempos e movimentos perfeitamente quantificáveis. Chamaremos de tarefas elementares (TE) a tais unidades de mão-de-obra.

Consideremos, agora, os materiais aplicados durante o processo produtivo. Chamaremos de itens as unidades desse insumo, as quais são, também, suscetíveis de quantificação.', '[-0.03290483,0.03790314,-0.011105234,-0.039623678,0.030624438,-0.035764463,0.099154204,0.07964308,0.041469906,0.083323136,0.08986949,-0.077281706,0.020208763,-0.016614117,-0.013490302,0.024685169,-0.021733584,-0.008307133,-0.033652503,0.06384129,0.15446691,-0.07689785,-0.07896151,0.06061702,-0.117578104,0.049914155,-0.041759904,0.038987666,-0.02832215,-0.0780138,-0.071831286,0.049801275,0.088469476,-0.015717555,0.02034806,0.059639778,-0.0032442356,0.012053872,-0.03714309,0.06358628,-0.0151277995,0.05241538,-0.05244318,-0.0798086,0.008575404,-0.05568053,0.08883546,-0.035741128,-0.04013728,-0.014576595,0.02553393,0.04757935,-0.05194707,0.042733185,-0.057024233,-0.040652778,0.030899286,-0.008069314,-0.06332566,0.026163714,-0.07513444,0.046447616,-0.02388848,0.042196497,0.07334883,0.022362998,0.003201716,0.0076187993,-0.098751575,0.05377987,0.0033333,-0.037406556,-0.012739374,0.018879412,-0.005995515,0.057835873,0.019093188,-0.0038240317,-0.04090714,-0.09142669,-0.03992766,-0.0011758923,-0.023915052,-0.091296636,0.022403963,0.047406517,-0.021851497,-0.01483996,0.07017177,-0.007000764,-0.009548159,0.03809874,-0.114671424,-0.0025998643,0.042184483,0.013463502,0.020915475,-0.0052835224,0.028614014,-0.04827236,0.03915498,0.044884022,-0.036098663,-0.048720963,-0.040440846,-0.04253028,0.013215667,-0.044464108,0.00775521,0.12331251,-0.08625535,-0.045933135,-0.054401126,0.032391224,-0.01836466,0.007628812,-0.05667969,-0.051203907,0.011134092,-0.07309399,0.012148695,-0.01834104,0.036126636,-0.025286352,-0.004611228,-0.06665486,0.044173516,9.302568e-33,-0.020526778,-0.06674509,-0.009701152,0.02201808,-0.008617041,0.030182151,-0.050162878,0.022734655,0.108561754,0.0316127,-0.11339514,0.07360713,-0.008479122,0.024256779,0.11929444,0.028232021,0.012658576,-0.034073792,0.0098815765,-0.006597946,-0.06476962,0.024