INSERT INTO book_pages (page_number, section, content, embedding, inserted_at, updated_at) VALUES (248, 'Página 248', 'rão ser corrigidos (equivale a desligar o piloto-automático e voltar à pilotagem manual).

A segunda inferência decorre, ainda, de uma relação matemática explicitada em g (t): quando a função de transferência da rede principal f (t) cresce, tornando-se muito maior do que 1, o valor de g (t) tende a se tornar independente de f (t) e negativo, pois a expressão passa a ser:

$$g (t) = -\frac{f (t)}{f (t). f (T)} = -\frac{1}{f (T)}$$

Em tal situação, a função global de transferência passa a ser quase totalmente condicionada pela rede de feedback f (T). Pensemos num sinal de entrada fraco, captado por um amplificador (rede principal) acoplado a uma rede de feedback. As saídas serão mantidas constantes em relação à entradas que, por qualquer causa, se mostrem flutuantes, e o sinal poderá ser ampliado sem que qualquer ruído ou falsa informação se amplifique. Estes permanecerão constantes e o efeito indesejável será minimizado, face à ampliação do sinal na rede principal que, assim, terá a sua pureza aumentada con', '[-0.0664739,-0.022292519,-0.08637617,-0.03594488,-0.04858667,0.028719721,0.01878307,0.06613483,0.049590174,0.09057257,0.1277891,-0.063637525,-0.00068180327,-0.007391158,-0.032234848,-0.018008364,0.05187576,0.027729984,-0.028491821,0.04007223,0.06789856,0.003276813,-0.040998977,0.043115843,-0.11238905,-0.037353538,-0.037572168,-0.0030484274,-0.09610708,-0.1416063,-0.06821511,0.038439307,0.017873,-0.05384183,-0.06606962,0.0169634,-0.03183318,-0.06639105,0.029237749,0.04431619,-0.045435306,0.049390033,0.010429936,-0.060461182,0.007853923,-0.01679541,0.04996051,0.037236616,-0.01484554,-0.022060677,0.07147491,0.06612286,-0.057433903,0.0037443074,0.007859921,-0.024950918,0.040989157,-0.0065717427,0.0053831832,0.0062674955,-0.050925285,0.008496558,-0.015369103,0.015571089,0.016667766,-0.049239237,0.013439542,-0.09231032,-0.018981157,-0.01638812,-0.04840981,-0.08333341,0.040034615,-0.035555687,0.020237437,0.06566569,-0.027820889,0.12948674,0.0015504974,-0.0070809466,0.061243035,-0.055393703,-0.010299217,-0.042580843,0.07374719,-0.021397462,-0.02654157,0.039259307,0.0391107,0.04575181,-0.0008154834,0.10942568,-0.103249855,-0.07447772,-0.018891426,-0.047589887,-0.024049358,0.024954123,0.0359523,0.014466055,0.029798998,0.024586372,-0.0117017375,0.052972756,-0.033264037,0.01194166,0.03561549,0.028978126,0.07662659,0.07156145,-0.14637071,0.035552736,-0.07756455,-0.004252388,-0.014839594,-0.019327678